# CPLNet - Pretrained Model Weights

## Overview

This repository provides the **best model weights** for the CPLNet architecture, which were saved during the training process based on optimal validation performance.

Due to the large file size (exceeding GitHub's standard limit), the file is hosted on **Baidu Netdisk**.

---

## Download Instructions

You can download the pretrained weights using the following link and extraction code:

- **Link**: [https://pan.baidu.com/s/1yER1d9xi8za_8rBieKQVnA?pwd=49fk](https://pan.baidu.com/s/1yER1d9xi8za_8rBieKQVnA?pwd=49fk)
- **Extraction Code (提取码)**: `49fk`
